<h3 class="headline-28">Science says: "I&rsquo;m thinking about how you are feeling."</h3>
<div class="entry-content --sm">
<p>People&rsquo;s brains are often irrational. Approaching communications as if our brains are rational and lead with facts over emotion means you&rsquo;ll miss opportunities to connect with and motivate your audiences. Check out how different people behave and how to encourage them to think and act the way you want. This table13 offers examples of psychological insights you may encounter. Some help you, and some make your communications more challenging. Knowing what you have to work with will help you create strategies that will work.</p>
</div>
